graph LR
    subgraph underfitting["과소적합 (Underfitting)"]
        A1[높은 편향<br/>낮은 분산]
        A2[학습/검증 손실<br/>모두 높음]
    end

    subgraph optimal["적정 적합 (Optimal)"]
        B1[적절한 균형]
        B2[학습/검증 손실<br/>모두 낮음]
    end

    subgraph overfitting["과적합 (Overfitting)"]
        C1[낮은 편향<br/>높은 분산]
        C2[학습 손실 낮음<br/>검증 손실 높음]
    end

    underfitting --> optimal --> overfitting

    subgraph prevention["과적합 방지 기법"]
        direction TB
        D1[Dropout]
        D2[BatchNorm]
        D3[Weight Decay]
        D4[Early Stopping]
        D5[Data Augmentation]
    end

    overfitting -.->|적용| prevention
    prevention -.->|개선| optimal

    style underfitting fill:#ffcdd2
    style optimal fill:#c8e6c9
    style overfitting fill:#fff9c4
    style prevention fill:#e1bee7
